&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Creative Fabrica&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Creative Fabrica is a subscription platform serving millions of creators, designers, and crafters worldwide. We&#39;re built on the principle that everyone can be creative. We remove what stands in the way: expensive software, technical expertise, and time-consuming production.&lt;/p&gt;
